data.description: This fully renovated ranch style home is a hidden gem located just 20 minutes east of DSM. The open floor plan with elevated ceilings & gorgeous LVP flooring throughout gives a spacious feel. The beautiful kitchen includes an enormous island with undermounted sink & handcrafted, concrete countertops; antique white soft close cabinets; all new appliances (< 1 year) including a gas range with direct vent hood & a convenient pot filler spigot; beautiful brick backsplash with floating shelves; & a large dining area big enough for the whole family. The large living room has a beautiful shiplap wall with built-in shelves, natural wood mantle, & an electric fireplace. The spare bedrooms & bath are nice sized with an updated full bath that includes a new vanity, mirror, light fixtures & a tile surround shower. The spacious master bedroom opens to an amazing private master bath with barn doors, separate his/her vanities, tile flooring, soaking tub, & an enormous walk-in shower with dual showerheads. The amazing walk-in closet also includes built-in wood shelving.  The attached 2-car garage opens to a nice mud room with built-in lockers, separate closet system, & convenient laundry with shelving. The covered front deck has a porch swing, is ramped for easy access, & overlooks a fully fenced front yard, great for kids or pets. A new AC unit & tons of other upgrades. Located in the wonderful small town of Monroe & just a few blocks from the high school, library, & public square.
